, these meticulous transcriptions are accompanied by a bibliography and filmography.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aMotion picture plays. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / General.2bisacsh  aamerica.  aamerican filmmakers.  aamerican institutions.  aamerican society.  aannotated.  acinema.  acritical introduction.  adocumentaries.  aemmy winners.  afamous filmmakers.  afeature length documentaries.  afilm criticism.  afilm critics.  afilm editing.  afilm scholars.  afilm studies.  afilm transcriptions.  afilmmakers.  afilmography.  afrederick wiseman.  ahigh school ii.  ahigh school.  aperforming arts.  apublic housing.  asocial life.  asound.  astudents and teachers.  atiticut follies.  awelfare.1 aGrant, Barry Keith, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aWiseman, Frederick, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z978311069042240uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052093870040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520938700423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520938700/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles